## ðŸ“™ Advanced Guide (docs/advanced.md)

### Presets
- Control resolution, duration, disparity
- Batch export supported

### Depth Masks
- White = closer
- Black = background
- No shadows

### Custom Animations
- Procedural generators
- JSON-driven presets
- Walking cat example

### Export Formats
- MP4 (H.264)
- Shorts (9:16)
- High bitrate presets

